R code for data exploration of www.ravelry.com, a social network around knitting. For more details, check out my blog: datasock.wordpress.com.

In order to use the code, you will most of the time need API access; you can register in the Ravelry API group at http://www.ravelry.com/groups/ravelry-api

warning: rav.r is just a bunch of notes in code form ...